## App Breakdown:

### 1. users/ - User Management
- User profiles (Patient, Therapist, Admin)
- Profile management
- User preferences

### 2. authentication/ - Authentication & Authorization
- JWT token management
- Login/logout endpoints
- Password reset functionality
- Permission classes

### 3. sessions/ - Therapy Sessions
- Session creation and management
- QR code generation for session linking
- Audio file handling
- Session analytics and insights

### 4. transcription/ - AI Transcription
- Audio processing pipeline
- Speaker diarization
- Transcription storage
- Emotion analysis

### 5. soap_notes/ - SOAP Notes
- SOAP note generation
- Templates and formatting
- Clinical documentation
- Version control for notes

### 6. patient_history/ - Patient History & Mood Tracking
- Mood journaling
- Historical data storage
- Progress tracking
- Reflection prompts

### 7. core/ - Shared Components
- Common utilities
- Base models
- Shared serializers
- Custom middleware